IN RE: DUVALL 372P17-1 Supreme Court of North Carolina. November 7, 2017 Daniel P. O'Brien, Special Deputy Attorney General, David Learner, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina. Kenneth Kelly Duvall, for Duvall, Kenneth Kelly.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 6th of November 2017 by Petitioner for Default Judgment:

"Motion Denied by order of the Court in conference, this the 7th of November 2017."
